{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "本章标题\"天池人\"，分两条线展开。白天，简怀萱劝芮玮善待未婚妻刘育芷，芮玮心生同情却苦于身份不能表露。夜晚，芮玮前往后山拜会喻百龙，喻百龙原欲传授三招绝学，得知芮玮已从简召舞处学会后大失所望，转而倾囊相授自己最精妙的\"玄妙三十掌\"，此掌法源于易经演变，步法玄妙。芮玮经四夜苦练已颇具规模。四天后，黑堡十三高手来犯——天魔黄温凯、地魔那印远、人魔柯轻农率九大蛇将围府。简老夫人故意只命芮玮一人应敌，意图借刀杀人。夏诗不顾死活相随，简怀萱亦违母命出府助阵。芮玮镇定心神，以简召舞的傲慢姿态应对黄温凯的试探，三魔被其气势所慑不敢轻举妄动。黄温凯假意讨还\"失物\"，实则率众里应外合攻入天池府放火。芮玮面临十二高手合围，以恩公所传三招应战，黑堡三魔抽出白骨剑布下\"天地人三才绝阵\"，战斗一触即发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一上午没见到大哥，是不是呆在刘姐姐的房间里呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么对大哥淘气，早上推大哥进去，差点和她撞个满怀……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她……她……她是谁呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我得揍你一顿屁股才行！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这么大了，哪能再打屁股……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你要对刘姐姐好一点！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我几时对她坏啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刘姐姐来了一年多，自从爸爸去世后，你就没见她过，若非今天我推你去见她，算来只在爸爸未去世前见她一面，你要对她好，会不去见她？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "应该对她好啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来嘛！刘姐姐又温柔又贤慧，大哥应对她好！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她还是个十分美丽的姑娘……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刘姐姐既有这么多好处，大哥以后可要对她好啊？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我会的！我会的！我会对她好的……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎能对她好呢？我并非真是她的未婚夫，但是恩公为什么不对她好呢？其中有什么原因呢？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你什么时候来的？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈才来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人老了便不中用，竟没听出来你的声音！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈心有所思，自然听觉失去灵敏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会！不会！我往昔决不会如此。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你来是向我学功夫的，我怎么自个先坍自己的台，来！来！我把三招演给你看，这三招是药兄独到之学……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看得如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三招芮玮会使。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？你会？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三招恩公教过我，故而会使！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我以为世上真有这等聪颖资高的人，看来是难求了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈资质鲁钝，这三招恩公教了很久，才会使。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你会了这三招，足以对付江湖一流高手，我对黑堡曾有所闻，就是堡主林三寒亲自来，在这三招中也无法胜你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三招真有如此厉害？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当年药兄独会关洛英雄时，关洛二十一位武林高手向他挑战，那时药兄仅以这三招一一将他们打败，他们竭尽所能也无法在这三招中逃过，败得心服口服，一时药兄这三招名震江湖，成为药兄的武功标帜，召舞这孩子将这三招传你，一能使你防身，再者你出这三招，别人便不会怀疑你是伪装的简公子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑堡来犯时，我就使出这三招，谢谢老前辈的指点。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既会这三招，我得教你一套别种武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我回去将这三招好好体会，不用再麻烦老前辈。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那怎么成，若不教你一套武功，二掌一脚之过，永记在心中，我就睡觉也睡不安稳！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还是勤练这三招的好，前辈教我新武功，我若学不精，到时间，反丢了前辈的脸，不如以后再学。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧不起我的武功吗？你以为会了三招就够了吗？我这武功你不用学精，只要学会，别说丢脸，光彩可大了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈尽力学习……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来传你一套掌法，名叫……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这套掌法名叫玄妙三十掌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信你能看得懂。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈指示，晚辈恭听！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这套掌法学问很深，主在步子的走动，其中之玄妙，出自易经的演变。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仅一晚的时间，你能练得这样，大出我之意料，如此下去，数天后黑堡来犯时，你不必再惧怕了！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子！公子！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是关照你们在我睡觉时，不要进来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奴婢有急事奉告！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事，你慢慢说。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫人……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你讲话不要怕啊！我也不会责备你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫人说要公子去应敌。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？应敌？是不是……敌人来了？……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们来了几人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像来了十多个……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了十多个，只……只叫我一人去应敌，这……这……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫人不准别人帮你，我……我……去帮你……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕老夫人罚你吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……不怕……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你随我去，只要我今日不死，尔后决不叫你再做卑贱之事！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑堡来人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再不出来，莫怪我们放火啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子，让奴婢来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你叹什么气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你来做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可是想帮我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥只要见你关心着我就可以了，母亲既有命令，你还是不要违背，乖乖地回去。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不！我要跟大哥出去！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还以为只有夏诗向着我，现在又有你，只要这样就好了。你要帮我，大哥反而不安，快回去吧！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不帮大哥，出去看看总行吧？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夏诗，开门！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在才出来吗！我还以为天池府都是缩头乌龟的人物。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你骂谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天池府乌龟号的人物，只剩下一个了吗。怎么来了两个女娃？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "瘦高人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你看谁来了？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还没有死！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们公子活得好好的，你们要是怕公子，也用不着咒他死啊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子姓什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我哥哥当然姓简！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敢情那个姓芮的小子入赘天池府，做了你的丈夫，才改姓简！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞎说八道，我家小姐待字闺房，哪曾有了丈夫！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有丈夫刚好！正好跟她这个假哥哥偷偷摸摸……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹妹回来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哥哥好好打他们一顿，他们太欺侮人了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你退到后面，大哥自有计较！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好亲热啊！好亲热啊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们可是黑堡来的吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_yin_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "那印远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芮玮，见着咱们，还不跪下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是芮玮？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子高名？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们配问本公子的名字吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_qing_nong",
      "speaker_name": "柯轻农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓芮的，别装蒜？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说有帮江湖人物要来本府骚扰，家母说那帮江湖人物都是些跳梁小丑，你一个人出去应付就得了，本公子出来时还以为要费一番手脚，哪知是一群疯子，穷嚷乱嚷的，早知就用不着出来了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下可是大公子简召舞吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑堡有个使唤的小子，长得和公子一模一样，兄弟们猛然一见，引起误会，尚望公子多多包涵！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既见本公子，还不跪下！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_yin_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "那印远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢叫我们跪下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二弟，不要多嘴！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本堡堡主吩咐在下们前来，主在取回失物，并无他意，刚刚多有得罪之处，公子大量，请宽宥则个！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本府世家，会取贵堡的失物，简直是笑话！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那件失物价值连城，是令尊未为宰相时至本堡取去，当时公子尚未出世，当不知晓。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是家父取去，为何当时不来取回，延至如今！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个……这个……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_yin_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "那印远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算那时不敢来，现在就敢来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_qing_nong",
      "speaker_name": "柯轻农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们现在看透了天池府，没有一个能人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "堡主说天池府在武林中占着领导的地位，黑堡自不敢轻易而来，此次前来，亦不敢冒犯，仅求将失物归还。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天池府再没有人，也不会将黑堡看在眼下！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个自然！那个自然！谁不知天池府无论婢女，仆人，就是三尺童子，亦然身怀绝艺，二弟、三弟不知好歹，说话轻重不分，公子见谅！公子见谅！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且说来，天池府取去贵堡何物？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那件物品贵重无比！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再贵重的物品，天池府也不稀罕！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是这件物品非同小可……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且说出名称，果真是黑堡的东西，立即归还！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当真吗……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那件东西，便是天池府的宝藏！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么宝藏！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁不知天池府宝藏无尽，取之不竭，尤其是武学奇书！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哥哥！哥哥！他们都侵入家里去了，快回去帮忙！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "久闻大公子武学高超，今日让在下们见识见识！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹妹，夏诗，你们先冲回去帮忙，留我在这里应付！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪有那么容易，黑堡不来则已，既来就不是弱手，天池府再强也不是黑堡十年预备的对手，快快纳命来吧！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个简公子，竟敢以空拳对敌，敢情怕活得不耐烦了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们快走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等大哥打败他们，我们一起走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们一定不是公子的对手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日叫你见见天地人三才绝阵的厉害。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    }
  ],
